algorithm: The new algorithm involves calculating a score for each bin by dividing the square root of the remaining capacity of the bin by the logarithm of the reciprocal of the item size, and subtracting it from the maximum capacity of the bins.
code:
import numpy as np

def score(item, bins):
    max_capacity = np.max(bins)
    scores = (np.sqrt(bins) / np.log(1/item)) - max_capacity
    return scores
